===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|nyghtyngale}}, {{m|enm|nightingale}}, {{m|enm|niȝtingale}}, alteration (with intrusive ''n'') of {{m|enm|nyghtgale}}, {{m|enm|nightegale}}, from {{inh|en|ang|nihtegala}}, {{m|ang|nihtegale||nightingale; night-raven|lit=night-singer}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*nahtigalā||nightingale}}, equivalent to {{compound|en|night|gale}}. Cognate with {{cog|stq|Noachtegoal||nightingale}}, {{cog|nl|nachtegaal||nightingale}}, {{cog|nds-de|Nachtigall||nightingale}}, {{cog|de|Nachtigall||nightingale}}, {{cog|da|nattergal||nightingale}}, {{cog|sv|näktergal||nightingale}}, {{cog|is|næturgali||nightingale}}.

